If you want to stay right in the heart of attractions, you need to stay at an older or more expensive hotel but if you don't mind walking a little, then Una Hotel is the right place to stay.	If you are looking for a modern hotel to stay in while visiting Rome the Una would be a good choice.	We would definitely return to this hotel if we were in Rome again and will try other hotels within the Una Group.	Would stay in hotel again and only wished that we had stayed in UNA Hotel in Milan on the next stop on our visit of Italy.